 succession of new tasks. Our empirical conclusions are\nconsistently supported by experiments on simulated manipulation tasks, and by\n52 unique fine-tuning experiments on a real robotic grasping system pre-trained\non 580,000 grasps.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Apr 2020 17:57:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 31 Jul 2020 13:43:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-03"}
