 to a\nfully dynamic algorithm by enriching a well-known 'decremental to fully\ndynamic' reduction with a new bootstrapping idea to recursively employ a fully\ndynamic algorithm instead of a static one in this reduction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Apr 2020 22:01:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Apr 2020 12:41:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-24"}
